that's their role.

00:10:32.125 --> 00:10:34.976
Never thought it would end up in my lap.

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:37.559
But I remember in early April 2006,

00:10:37.583 --> 00:10:40.101
I opened up my Blackberry,

00:10:40.125 --> 00:10:44.018
and I'm reading about
Greenpeace campaigners

00:10:44.042 --> 00:10:48.184
showing up in the UK by the dozens,

00:10:48.208 --> 00:10:50.184
dressed as chickens,

00:10:50.208 --> 00:10:52.476
having breakfast at McDonald's

00:10:52.500 --> 00:10:55.601
and chaining themselves
to the chairs and tables.

00:10:55.625 --> 00:10:57.518
So they got a lot of attention,

00:10:57.542 --> 00:10:59.393
including mine.

00:10:59.417 --> 00:11:02.351
And I was wondering if the report
